org.mitre.provenance.mediator

Class SimpleStringSurrogatePreference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mitre.provenance.mediator.ObjectPreference
      • org.mitre.provenance.mediator.SurrogatePreference
        • org.mitre.provenance.mediator.SimpleStringSurrogatePreference

  • public class SimpleStringSurrogatePreference
extends SurrogatePreference
    This is a class that will mediate various surrogates. I.e. given several different (surrogate) options for a data item, the most preferred surrogate will be returned. This implies a total ordering.
    Author:
    MDMORSE
